longBusinessSummary: Desert Gold Ventures Inc., an exploration stage company, engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral resource properties. The company primarily explores for gold ores. Its flagship project is the Senegal Mali Shear Zone project covering an area of 410 square kilometers located in Western Africa. The company is headquartered in Surrey, Canada.
